Comment: 0,0:22:41.63,0:22:44.43,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}跪{\k1}下{\k1}在{\k1}此{\k1}立{\k1}下{\k1}誓{\k1}言
Comment: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:48.56,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}伸{\k1}出{\k1}的{\k1}指{\k1}尖{\k1} {\k1}A{\k1}n{\k1}y{\k1}t{\k1}i{\k1}m{\k1}e{\k1},{\k1} {\k1}t{\k1}o{\k1}u{\k1}c{\k1}h{\k1}i{\k1}n{\k1}g{\k1} {\k1}y{\k1}o{\k1}u
Comment: 0,0:22:48.56,0:22:51.37,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}不{\k1}能{\k1}被{\k1}知{\k1}道{\k1}的{\k1}秘{\k1}密{\k1}任{\k1}务
Comment: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:57.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}二{\k1}人{\k1}犯{\k1}下{\k1}的{\k1}深{\k1}重{\k1}罪{\k1}孽{\k1}…
Comment: 0,0:22:57.81,0:23:01.37,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}循{\k1}环{\k1}往{\k1}复{\k1}的{\k1}世{\k1}界{\k1}线
Comment: 0,0:23:02.59,0:23:06.93,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}「{\k1}我{\k1}需{\k1}要{\k1}你{\k1}，{\k1}我{\k1}需{\k1}要{\k1}你{\k1}」{\k1}这{\k1}是{\k1}秘{\k1}密
Comment: 0,0:23:11.71,0:23:15.48,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}拜{\k1}托{\k1}请{\k1}不{\k1}要{\k1}停{\k1}下{\k1}来
Comment: 0,0:23:15.60,0:23:19.13,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}你{\k1}与{\k1}我{\k1}共{\k1}同{\k1}奏{\k1}响{\k1}的{\k1}旋{\k1}律
Comment: 0,0:23:25.62,0:23:29.57,OPCN,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\k1}时{\k1}刻{\k1}都{\k1}要{\k1}在{\k1}我{\k1}身{\k1}边
